A l'aide des <span style="color: rgb(0, 170, 255);">loi de Mayer</span>:&nbsp;\(C_P = C_V + nR\)<br>Def <span style="color: rgb(0, 170, 255);">coef adiabatique</span>:&nbsp;\(\gamma = \frac{C_P}{C_V}\)<br>Def Energie Interne et Enthalpie:&nbsp;\(\Delta_{AB}U = C_V T\)<br>\(\begin{aligned}
&amp;\begin{cases}
C_P = C_V + nR, \\
\gamma = \frac{C_P}{C_V}
\end{cases}
\quad \Rightarrow \quad
\begin{cases}
C_P = \gamma C_V, \\
\gamma C_V = C_V + nR
\end{cases} \\
&amp;\quad \Rightarrow \quad
\boxed{U = \frac{1}{\gamma - 1} nRT \quad \text{et} \quad H = \frac{\gamma}{\gamma - 1} nRT}.
\end{aligned}\)

